# 01 - Data

This folder contains the datasets used in the Retail Sales Performance & Profitability Analytics project.

## Folder Structure
- **Raw/**
  - Original unmodified datasets received from the source.
  - Used only for reference and audit purposes.
- **Cleaned/**
  - Processed and standardized datasets after Excel-based data cleaning.
  - Ready for SQL import and analytical modeling.

## Data Privacy Note
No confidential or personally identifiable information (PII) is included in this dataset.

